==Handing the completed folder over to Rat==
* '''Player:''' Hey, Rat! I got your pages back!
* '''Rat Burgiss:''' Excellent! I knew you could help! Let me take those from you, there.
* {{tact|gives=a [[full folder]] and extra pages (if present) to Rat Burgiss}}
* '''Rat Burgiss:''' Now, I liked the way you handled yourself on that last little 'mission' I gave you there, so I'm going to let you in on a little secret!
* '''Player:''' Wait! Wait! Let me guess! You're actually a rich prince in disguise who wants to help poor people like me!?
* '''Rat Burgiss:''' Uhhh...no. No, that's not it. You know, on second thought, I think I'll keep my secret for now. Look, instead, you can do another job for me.
* '''Player:''' All work and no play makes [player name] a dull adventurer!
* '''Rat Burgiss:''' Yes, well, I'm sure that may be the case. However, what I want you to do is take this letter to someone for me. It's in a different language so, trust me, you won't be able to read it.
* '''Rat Burgiss:''' Take it to a wizard named Surok Magis who resides in the Varrock Place Library. I'll see about some sort of reward for your work when I get myself sorted out here.
* {{tact|receives=a [[Letter to surok]]}}
* '''Player:''' Letter. Wizard. Varrock. Library. Got it!
* '''Rat Burgiss:''' Yes, good luck then.
* {{tact|end}}

